      <section eId="sec_7508">
        <num>7508</num>
        <heading>Award by confession</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_7508__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>When available. An award by\nconfession may be made for money due or to become due at any time before\nan award is otherwise made. The award shall be based upon a statement,\nverified by each party, containing an authorization to make the award,\nthe sum of the award or the method of ascertaining it, and the facts\nconstituting the liability.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_7508__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Time of award. The award may be made at any time within three\nmonths after the statement is verified.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_7508__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Person or agency making award.  The award may be made by an\narbitrator or by the agency or person named by the parties to designate\nthe abitrator.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
